OL,3,CDonald Trump claims he speaks for the
OL,4,CUK more than Prince Harry
OL,6,FDonald Trump has claimed he "speaks
OL,7,Ffor the UK more than Prince Harry"
OL,8,Fafter the Duke urged the US president
OL,9,Fto do more to end the war in Ukraine.
OL,11,FSpeaking on Thursday during a surprise
OL,12,Fvisit to Ukraine, Prince Harry urged
OL,13,Fboth Trump and Vladimir Putin to end
OL,14,Fthe war.
OL,16,FWhen asked in the Oval Office about
OL,17,Fthe comments, Trump said: "I know one
OL,18,Fthing, Prince Harry is not speaking
OL,19,Ffor the UK, that's for sure, I think I
OL,20,Fspeak for the UK more than Prince
OL,21,FHarry, but I appreciate his advice."
