OL,3,CDonald Trump claims he speaks for the
OL,4,CUK more than Prince Harry
OL,6,FThe Duke of Sussex was invited to
OL,7,Fdeliver the keynote speech at the Kyiv
OL,8,FSecurity Forum, which is taking place
OL,9,Fdespite ongoing Russian attacks on
OL,10,FUkraine.
OL,12,FPrince Harry arriving in Ukraine
OL,14,FThe prince did not mention Donald
OL,15,FTrump by name, but he said he had a
OL,16,Fmessage for the "American leadership".
OL,26,@xD@QOUxD@eO]
