PN,31303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1777028572
OL,3,CDonald Trump claims he speaks for the
OL,4,CUK more than Prince Harry
OL,6,FHarry said the US - his adopted
OL,7,Fcountry - has a "singular role" in
OL,8,Fthis conflict because, when Ukraine
OL,9,Fagreed to give up its nuclear weapons,
OL,10,FAmerica had pledged to protect
OL,11,FUkraine's borders and its sovereignty.
OL,13,FHe told the Trump administration:
OL,14,F"This is a moment for American
OL,15,Fleadership ` a moment for America to
OL,16,Fshow that it can honour its
OL,17,Finternational treaty obligations - not
OL,18,Fout of charity, but out of its
OL,19,Fenduring role in global security and
OL,20,Fstrategic stability."
OL,26,@oD@QOUoD@_O]|D@UO]
