OL,3,CDonald Trump claims he speaks for the
OL,4,CUK more than Prince Harry
OL,6,FTrump was also speaking ahead of the
OL,7,FKing's state visit to the United
OL,8,FStates next week.
OL,10,FCharles and Camilla arrive in the US
OL,11,Fon Monday for a four-day visit during
OL,12,Fwhich they will meet Trump.
OL,14,FThey will also be guests of honour at
OL,15,Fa White House banquet, and Charles has
OL,16,Fbeen invited to address a joint
OL,17,Fmeeting of the US Congress.
OL,19,FTheir visit coincides with the US's
OL,20,F250th birthday, with events planned
OL,21,Fthroughout the year.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
