PN,31305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1777028572
OL,3,CDonald Trump claims he speaks for the
OL,4,CUK more than Prince Harry
OL,6,FThis is the first time a British
OL,7,Fmonarch has visited the US since Queen
OL,8,FElizabeth in 2007.
OL,10,FThe King and Queen will be welcomed to
OL,11,FWashington DC on April 27, with a
OL,12,Fprivate tea at the White House hosted
OL,13,Fby the President and First Lady.
OL,15,FThere will also be a formal ceremonial
OL,16,Fmilitary review the next day in the
OL,17,FWhite House grounds, plus a bilateral
OL,18,Fmeeting between King Charles and
OL,19,FPresident Trump.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/6
