OL,3,CDonald Trump claims he speaks for the
OL,4,CUK more than Prince Harry
OL,6,FFollowing the speech to senators and
OL,7,Frepresentatives in Congress, the King
OL,8,Fand Queen will attend a state dinner
OL,9,Fat the White House with speeches from
OL,10,Fboth principals.
